WEBVTT

01:52.280 --> 01:57.509
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.660 --> 02:01.920
[Episode 25]

02:08.190 --> 02:09.150
Tian Xing.

02:11.120 --> 02:12.190
Tian Xing!

02:15.310 --> 02:16.630
My sister isn't here.

02:17.710 --> 02:18.710
Where is she?

02:20.870 --> 02:22.870
We came to save them out of kindness,

02:22.870 --> 02:24.560
but they want to ruin themselves.

02:24.560 --> 02:26.620
Might as well let them have their way.

02:28.630 --> 02:30.470
How can you be so heartless?

02:30.910 --> 02:32.770
The sweet wormwood medicine we prepared

02:32.770 --> 02:34.220
was for saving everyone.

02:34.560 --> 02:36.079
If they don't go out now,

02:36.079 --> 02:37.740
won't the medicine be wasted?

02:39.690 --> 02:40.640
Right.

02:40.660 --> 02:42.120
The life-saving medicine

02:42.130 --> 02:43.500
will all go to waste.

02:43.690 --> 02:44.690
Folks,

02:44.790 --> 02:46.350
in the current situation,

02:46.370 --> 02:48.140
even if you don't leave with us,

02:48.170 --> 02:49.680
won't it just be a dead end?

02:52.250 --> 02:53.980
I believe you. I'll go with you.

02:55.760 --> 02:56.980
-Let's go.
-I'll go with you.

02:56.980 --> 02:57.680
Let's hurry.

02:57.680 --> 02:59.120
-I believe you.
-I believe you. Let's go.

02:59.120 --> 02:59.910
I'll go out too.

02:59.910 --> 03:00.750
Let's go.

03:01.220 --> 03:02.220
OK, I believe you.

03:03.730 --> 03:05.380
I'll go out with you.

03:05.490 --> 03:06.540
Can you really cure us?

03:06.540 --> 03:07.270
Don't worry.

03:07.560 --> 03:08.870
You will be cured.

03:09.000 --> 03:09.530
Come.

03:09.680 --> 03:10.150
Come.

03:10.710 --> 03:12.150
Everyone, come this way.

03:12.150 --> 03:13.680
-Careful.
-Be careful.

03:15.120 --> 03:16.120
Follow us!

03:16.120 --> 03:17.310
Follow us.

03:17.630 --> 03:18.240
Hurry.

03:19.400 --> 03:21.240
-Keep up, everyone.
-Keep up.

03:21.710 --> 03:23.240
-Come.
-Let's go.

03:26.350 --> 03:27.880
What's going on?

03:27.910 --> 03:29.420
What happened?

04:02.990 --> 04:03.960
Chief.

04:03.980 --> 04:05.320
Some of the commoners escaped,

04:05.320 --> 04:07.010
but we caught the one we need.

04:09.080 --> 04:10.200
You may leave.

04:10.220 --> 04:10.820
Yes.

04:16.440 --> 04:17.430
Strange noises from the cave.

04:17.430 --> 04:18.890
There must be a situation.

04:19.760 --> 04:21.350
Guardian Corps, at my command.

04:21.350 --> 04:23.350
Follow me into the cave to save them.

04:38.640 --> 04:39.930
Watch... Watch out!

04:42.270 --> 04:43.930
There are people in the rocks!

05:49.520 --> 05:50.930
It's almost time.

05:51.530 --> 05:52.570
Let's begin.

07:13.600 --> 07:14.350
Fan Yun.

07:17.050 --> 07:18.000
Hey.

07:18.100 --> 07:19.000
Hey!

07:19.270 --> 07:19.960
Wake up.

07:31.000 --> 07:31.800
Fan Yun.

07:32.510 --> 07:33.180
Fan Yun!

07:33.200 --> 07:34.060
Stop shouting.

07:34.510 --> 07:35.640
It's dream sorcery.

07:36.310 --> 07:37.240
What is that?

07:37.560 --> 07:38.820
Every Jianghu wanderer knows

07:38.820 --> 07:40.640
it has existed since ancient times.

07:40.640 --> 07:42.630
It's originally
a way to treat illnesses,

07:42.630 --> 07:44.170
but in malicious hands,

07:44.200 --> 07:45.560
hypnotic illusions can be created

07:45.560 --> 07:47.290
to manipulate people's minds.

07:56.440 --> 07:58.060
I never thought there'd be a day

07:58.060 --> 07:59.720
when I have to team up with you.

08:00.120 --> 08:01.650
Count how many there are on your side.

08:01.650 --> 08:02.650
What's the point?

08:03.280 --> 08:05.010
Just take down as many as we can.

08:22.460 --> 08:23.420
Fan Yun.

08:24.250 --> 08:25.120
Fan Yun.

08:38.360 --> 08:39.120
Mother!

08:40.200 --> 08:40.830
Mother!

08:43.980 --> 08:44.550
Mother.

08:45.610 --> 08:47.210
Why can't I grasp you?

08:48.100 --> 08:49.410
My silly child,

08:50.040 --> 08:51.480
it's because I'm dead.

08:52.290 --> 08:53.370
Dead?

08:54.920 --> 08:56.040
Impossible.

08:56.410 --> 08:57.530
You're standing

08:58.010 --> 08:59.520
right in front of me.

09:01.790 --> 09:04.050
Do you really want me
to come back to life?

09:05.870 --> 09:06.630
Mother,

09:07.000 --> 09:07.910
I do.

09:16.250 --> 09:17.170
Look.

09:18.480 --> 09:19.960
You know what to do,

09:20.330 --> 09:21.640
my dear child.

09:28.710 --> 09:29.710
But

09:30.280 --> 09:32.440
you must live on well.

09:35.400 --> 09:36.360
You alone

09:37.030 --> 09:38.430
must live the lives of two

09:38.670 --> 09:40.340
or even three people.

09:41.840 --> 09:43.880
Let the two of us live to the fullest.

09:47.630 --> 09:49.550
If you ever miss me in the future,

09:50.230 --> 09:51.660
think of these words.

10:02.630 --> 10:03.540
What's wrong,

10:03.630 --> 10:04.630
my baby?

10:06.240 --> 10:07.510
Why did you stop?

10:08.630 --> 10:10.200
Don't you want to save me?

10:11.440 --> 10:12.000
No.

10:12.600 --> 10:13.150
No.

10:14.120 --> 10:15.320
You're not my mother.

10:16.240 --> 10:17.740
My mother is someone

10:17.770 --> 10:19.010
who'd brave death

10:19.140 --> 10:20.670
and risk everything for me.

10:20.960 --> 10:22.460
She'd never take my life.

10:24.310 --> 10:26.170
You're definitely not my mother.

10:31.390 --> 10:32.540
What are you doing?

10:35.130 --> 10:37.040
You ungrateful wench.

10:47.560 --> 10:48.160
Let's go!

11:06.820 --> 11:07.910
Qi Zheng!

11:08.390 --> 11:09.200
Qi Zheng!

11:50.200 --> 11:50.960
Qi Zheng!

11:52.460 --> 11:54.080
Fan Yun has done you no wrong.

11:54.550 --> 11:55.850
Why do you want to take her life?

11:55.850 --> 11:56.890
She's a witch!

11:56.910 --> 11:58.310
As the Spirit Immortal Sect's chief,

11:58.310 --> 12:00.510
it's my duty to eliminate evil
for the people!

12:00.510 --> 12:01.960
What a load of nonsense.

12:02.250 --> 12:03.440
Come to your senses!

12:03.510 --> 12:04.600
You keep saying it's for the people,

12:04.600 --> 12:05.820
but what people?

12:06.110 --> 12:07.970
You exploit their desire to live,

12:08.290 --> 12:10.890
just to destroy
their trust in the Nine Cities.

12:11.270 --> 12:12.910
You make them lose their homes,

12:12.910 --> 12:14.120
and even their lives.

12:15.120 --> 12:16.370
You preach morality

12:16.520 --> 12:17.950
but practice vice!

12:17.970 --> 12:18.830
Cut the crap.

12:18.870 --> 12:20.540
Only I can save them.

13:00.270 --> 13:01.120
Tian Yue,

13:01.140 --> 13:01.900
come out!

13:06.820 --> 13:07.640
Zheng!

13:07.920 --> 13:08.550
Wine!

13:09.690 --> 13:10.400
Wine!

13:11.070 --> 13:11.590
Hurry!

13:12.310 --> 13:13.240
Give me the wine!

13:13.670 --> 13:14.270
Hurry!

13:15.070 --> 13:15.710
Wine!

13:25.970 --> 13:26.930
Qi Zheng—

13:33.560 --> 13:34.800
Qi Zheng is right.

13:34.820 --> 13:36.020
Everything you've done

13:36.020 --> 13:37.900
has been entirely self-serving.

13:38.880 --> 13:41.080
You just want to control the commoners!

14:23.830 --> 14:24.620
Tian Yue!

14:25.350 --> 14:27.150
I run into you every time I show up.

14:27.150 --> 14:28.410
What a pain in the neck.

14:33.760 --> 14:34.970
Where is Tian Xing?

15:05.390 --> 15:06.200
Let's go.

15:16.750 --> 15:17.720
Miss Suyin.

15:20.190 --> 15:21.330
Where are the governor and Lady Fan Yun?

15:21.330 --> 15:22.320
I... I don't know.

15:22.320 --> 15:22.980
When I woke up,

15:22.980 --> 15:24.310
they were already gone.

15:26.110 --> 15:27.620
Alright. Then,

15:27.640 --> 15:28.640
you take Suyin out.

15:28.640 --> 15:29.570
I'll go find them.

15:29.570 --> 15:30.940
-OK.
-I'll go with you.

15:36.520 --> 15:37.950
Take the rest of the people out now.

15:37.950 --> 15:38.610
-Now.
-Yes.

15:38.670 --> 15:39.320
Hurry!

15:39.320 --> 15:40.030
Move along!

15:41.760 --> 15:42.800
Go, go.

15:42.820 --> 15:43.490
Come on, let's go.

15:43.490 --> 15:44.450
Hurry.

16:08.810 --> 16:09.870
Qi Zheng, look out!

17:09.400 --> 17:10.359
Sister,

17:10.390 --> 17:11.770
don't leave me.

17:13.000 --> 17:13.930
Don't be scared.

17:15.130 --> 17:16.440
I'll be right back.

17:38.890 --> 17:39.810
Your Excellency.

17:39.810 --> 17:40.370
Gao Ran.

17:40.580 --> 17:41.310
Lady Fan Yun.

17:42.520 --> 17:43.390
Gao Ran,

17:43.420 --> 17:44.180
your hand...

17:45.570 --> 17:47.590
Desheng has brought the people
to the cave entrance.

17:47.590 --> 17:48.720
Please don't worry.

17:50.570 --> 17:51.490
I'm so glad that

17:51.830 --> 17:52.750
you're both OK.

18:04.620 --> 18:05.540
Sister!

18:10.590 --> 18:11.440
Tian Xing!

18:11.880 --> 18:12.510
Suyin.

18:16.260 --> 18:16.910
Sister...

18:18.400 --> 18:19.130
How is it you?

18:20.590 --> 18:21.640
Why is it you?

18:25.180 --> 18:25.910
In the end...

18:26.840 --> 18:29.010
I was the one who was wrong.

18:31.510 --> 18:33.070
I deserve this.

18:36.430 --> 18:37.880
Tian Xing...

18:39.050 --> 18:40.250
Tian Xing...

18:46.230 --> 18:47.420
Sorry.

18:49.030 --> 18:50.310
I'm sorry.

18:51.820 --> 18:52.970
I...

18:55.230 --> 18:57.320
have to leave you

18:58.070 --> 18:59.390
-again.
-No...

19:21.150 --> 19:22.950
Sister!

19:24.280 --> 19:25.950
Sister...

20:31.840 --> 20:32.640
You're here.

20:32.670 --> 20:33.670
Your Excellency.

20:34.160 --> 20:35.400
Come, sit.

20:37.150 --> 20:37.700
Here,

20:38.020 --> 20:40.530
try the calming soup I just made.

20:40.550 --> 20:41.710
Drink it while it's hot.

20:41.710 --> 20:43.170
It'll soothe your nerves.

20:45.300 --> 20:46.680
You just got out
of the Spirit Immortal Sect.

20:46.680 --> 20:47.960
Are you hurt?

20:48.720 --> 20:49.770
I'm fine.

20:51.010 --> 20:51.860
How about you?

20:54.550 --> 20:55.440
I...

20:57.220 --> 20:58.980
Your Excellency must be fine.

20:59.590 --> 21:01.170
Otherwise, with your temper,

21:01.170 --> 21:03.120
even a tiny scratch on your finger would

21:03.120 --> 21:05.380
have you screaming everyone's ears off.

21:06.070 --> 21:07.400
You know what? I am hurt.

21:08.400 --> 21:09.860
Which finger was it again?

21:10.590 --> 21:11.200
This one!

21:11.430 --> 21:12.510
I just sprained it.

21:12.530 --> 21:13.620
It hurts so bad.

21:13.680 --> 21:14.790
Blow on it for me.

21:14.790 --> 21:15.940
I see you've changed.

21:15.940 --> 21:17.000
You're hurt, but you're

21:17.000 --> 21:18.260
not crying out in pain.

21:19.510 --> 21:21.080
Am I such a weak person?

21:21.750 --> 21:23.200
I was the one who
brought that sect's chief

21:23.200 --> 21:24.050
to justice.

21:24.230 --> 21:25.490
It was all thanks to me.

21:28.830 --> 21:29.800
I didn't expect

21:30.090 --> 21:31.950
the Spirit Immortal Sect's chief

21:32.020 --> 21:33.630
to be Tian Xing's sister.

21:34.260 --> 21:35.220
But

21:35.830 --> 21:37.440
I've never met her before.

21:37.710 --> 21:39.710
Why do you think she wanted me dead?

21:40.620 --> 21:41.600
She did it to

21:41.830 --> 21:43.160
sway public sentiment.

21:46.570 --> 21:47.840
This is also a lingering consequence

21:47.840 --> 21:48.860
for failing to dismantle

21:48.860 --> 21:50.440
the nobility in the Nine Cities.

21:50.440 --> 21:52.480
The commoners only turned to that sect

21:52.480 --> 21:54.080
because they felt hopeless.

21:54.830 --> 21:55.690
Tian Yang, too,

21:56.030 --> 21:58.310
must've endured abject poverty.

21:58.340 --> 22:00.310
She was able to grasp their mindset,

22:00.310 --> 22:01.590
shamelessly exploit their plight,

22:01.590 --> 22:03.390
and coax them into going astray.

22:03.610 --> 22:05.210
If they had any other choice,

22:05.230 --> 22:06.750
I believe the people of Yong City

22:06.750 --> 22:08.400
wouldn't have traded all of their money

22:08.400 --> 22:10.200
just for that little bit of hope.

22:13.270 --> 22:14.060
So,

22:14.550 --> 22:16.000
Your Excellency's reform

22:16.000 --> 22:17.270
is truly vital.

22:19.640 --> 22:20.880
Are you praising me?

22:22.580 --> 22:23.660
I...

22:25.240 --> 22:26.750
If Your Excellency thinks it's praise,

22:26.750 --> 22:27.790
then it is.

22:30.200 --> 22:31.730
Then I'll take it as praise.

22:36.590 --> 22:37.350
However,

22:38.680 --> 22:40.070
this trip to Yong City

22:40.750 --> 22:42.480
has really made me realize that

22:43.140 --> 22:45.350
every decision I make
and every word I say

22:45.350 --> 22:46.680
at the morning assembly

22:46.730 --> 22:49.430
has a profound impact on the commoners.

22:49.860 --> 22:52.190
So I must always
err on the side of caution.

22:52.420 --> 22:53.020
It has also

22:53.430 --> 22:54.980
really opened my eyes to the power

22:54.980 --> 22:56.310
of women's resilience.

22:57.350 --> 22:57.960
Like

22:58.440 --> 22:59.170
Chunxiu,

22:59.420 --> 23:00.260
Zhu Luan,

23:00.340 --> 23:01.130
and Suyin;

23:01.680 --> 23:02.830
they all played extraordinary roles

23:02.830 --> 23:04.290
in desperate situations.

23:04.590 --> 23:06.040
Truly admirable.

23:09.290 --> 23:10.420
Your Excellency has

23:10.720 --> 23:13.580
indeed achieved exceptional insight
and matured.

23:17.720 --> 23:19.920
Actually, you're the exceptional one.

23:20.440 --> 23:22.010
I thought it was bad enough

23:22.160 --> 23:24.420
that the nobles were eyeing you closely,

23:24.540 --> 23:26.310
but to think that even in Yong City,

23:26.310 --> 23:27.510
the sketchy Spirit Immortal Sect

23:27.510 --> 23:28.710
had their eyes on you.

23:29.090 --> 23:30.820
They say being by a ruler's side

23:30.880 --> 23:32.250
is like living with a tiger,

23:32.250 --> 23:34.380
but I think the opposite is true for us.

23:36.270 --> 23:37.790
It's getting late.

23:37.960 --> 23:39.620
I should head to the pharmacy.

23:40.550 --> 23:41.550
Also,

23:42.000 --> 23:43.160
actually...

23:44.800 --> 23:46.510
when it really hurts,

23:47.110 --> 23:48.640
you don't have to keep it in.

23:48.880 --> 23:49.530
I...

23:51.540 --> 23:53.470
You'd better put on some ointment.

23:55.230 --> 23:56.270
I'm not in pain.

23:57.130 --> 23:58.590
I'm really not in any pain.

24:02.270 --> 24:03.240
Fan Yun!

25:10.830 --> 25:11.830
Lady Fan Yun!

25:15.720 --> 25:17.570
Are you still mad at me?

25:20.820 --> 25:21.450
Yes.

25:22.110 --> 25:23.000
Of course.

25:25.430 --> 25:26.360
Yes.

25:26.680 --> 25:29.210
It's justified
no matter how much you hate me.

25:29.900 --> 25:31.590
After all, what I did

25:32.550 --> 25:33.830
was a capital crime.

25:38.240 --> 25:39.640
Are you leaving soon?

25:40.920 --> 25:42.520
I was sent here temporarily.

25:42.880 --> 25:44.480
I'll return to Ling'an soon.

25:44.960 --> 25:46.690
Thank you for all your efforts.

25:50.210 --> 25:51.290
Lady Fan Yun.

25:54.570 --> 25:56.290
Since I fled to Yong City,

25:57.060 --> 25:59.060
not a day goes by that I don't repent.

25:59.750 --> 26:02.160
No one here knows what I used to do.

26:03.570 --> 26:05.970
I've been dreaming of the day
I see you again

26:06.750 --> 26:09.010
so I could apologize to you in person.

26:14.120 --> 26:14.860
OK,

26:15.510 --> 26:16.640
I understand.

26:17.830 --> 26:19.490
Please take care of yourself.

26:19.510 --> 26:21.030
I'll stay in Yong City

26:21.050 --> 26:22.780
and properly atone for my sins.

26:30.750 --> 26:31.550
Suyin.

26:33.790 --> 26:35.250
Return to Ling'an with me.

26:37.440 --> 26:38.390
Lady Fan Yun,

26:38.750 --> 26:39.920
what did you say?

26:41.350 --> 26:43.590
While saving the people
from the plague in Yong City,

26:43.590 --> 26:45.120
you helped me save Tian Xing

26:45.200 --> 26:47.470
and took care of the patients
day and night;

26:47.470 --> 26:48.840
I know all of this.

26:51.030 --> 26:52.200
However,

26:52.640 --> 26:54.170
I don't think it was enough.

26:54.750 --> 26:55.480
So,

26:56.530 --> 26:58.010
return to Ling'an with me

26:58.790 --> 27:00.390
to atone for your sins there.

27:01.190 --> 27:02.600
Lady Fan Yun.

27:30.680 --> 27:32.200
Where am I?

27:32.760 --> 27:34.980
In your dream.

27:39.540 --> 27:40.410
Tian Yue?

27:42.110 --> 27:43.110
It's you.

27:43.640 --> 27:44.570
Why are you here?

27:44.970 --> 27:46.380
Didn't you call me here?

28:05.260 --> 28:06.540
It's so great to see you

28:07.070 --> 28:07.700
in person.

28:08.300 --> 28:11.060
♪ My heart is unwavering ♪

28:09.570 --> 28:10.250
Come on.

28:11.240 --> 28:12.030
Have a drink.

28:11.560 --> 28:15.070
♪ My dreams become wings ♪

28:12.600 --> 28:13.640
I don't drink.

28:14.400 --> 28:15.400
From now on,

28:15.450 --> 28:19.930
♪ What does it matter
if we fly against the wind? ♪

28:15.830 --> 28:16.880
you can drink.

28:20.820 --> 28:23.710
♪ The most ordinary desire ♪

28:23.730 --> 28:28.350
♪ Is worth lighting up ♪

28:28.380 --> 28:31.000
♪ With my life ♪

28:31.030 --> 28:33.700
♪ From then on ♪

28:33.730 --> 28:36.770
♪ Time left a glimmer of hope ♪

28:36.990 --> 28:45.740
♪ Take it as the glory of my journey ♪

28:44.830 --> 28:45.500
A destined

28:46.410 --> 28:47.340
reunion...

28:46.590 --> 28:52.170
♪ Face the light,
gaze ahead with brave eyes ♪

28:50.830 --> 28:51.550
Fears

28:52.110 --> 28:53.030
no goodbyes.

28:52.350 --> 28:56.550
♪ Let all darkness and hurt step aside ♪

28:56.570 --> 28:58.710
♪ It's unstoppable ♪

28:58.850 --> 29:04.540
♪ We chase the light and travel together ♪

28:59.920 --> 29:00.980
Stay where you are.

29:03.790 --> 29:04.790
Tian Xing.

29:04.760 --> 29:06.740
♪ Not considering how long the road is ♪

29:06.780 --> 29:10.780
♪ When looking back,
I'm still young and stubborn ♪

29:07.400 --> 29:08.610
I'll be watching you.

29:10.810 --> 29:12.610
You've got this.

29:10.810 --> 29:14.560
♪ Let the weathered past ♪

29:14.580 --> 29:17.080
♪ The places once journeyed ♪

29:17.100 --> 29:20.690
♪ Turn into myriad lights ♪

29:20.710 --> 29:25.810
♪ Just as I expected ♪

30:00.120 --> 30:00.840
Tian Xing,

30:00.870 --> 30:01.740
you're awake.

30:01.760 --> 30:02.510
Get up.

30:07.830 --> 30:08.890
You must be hungry.

30:14.130 --> 30:14.970
He's gone.

30:21.680 --> 30:22.830
Who's gone?

30:23.370 --> 30:24.330
A...

30:27.300 --> 30:28.020
friend.

30:31.000 --> 30:32.310
He just

30:33.400 --> 30:35.290
said goodbye to me in my dream.

30:37.490 --> 30:39.450
Now my sister's gone,

30:41.000 --> 30:42.070
and he's gone too.

30:46.240 --> 30:47.270
Tian Xing,

30:48.230 --> 30:50.520
you've already done your best.

30:51.830 --> 30:53.360
Besides, you still have...

30:54.920 --> 30:56.640
you still have Lady Fan Yun,

30:56.660 --> 30:57.790
Gao Ran,

30:58.110 --> 30:58.890
and...

31:01.310 --> 31:02.200
And you.

31:04.920 --> 31:05.830
Suyin,

31:07.570 --> 31:08.680
thank you.

31:17.260 --> 31:19.500
Are Shi's bedding and clean clothes

31:19.520 --> 31:21.080
all prepared?

31:21.550 --> 31:22.310
Rest assured, Master.

31:22.310 --> 31:23.070
I've packed them.

31:23.070 --> 31:24.280
I've packed plenty.

31:24.590 --> 31:26.200
I don't know why,

31:26.720 --> 31:28.750
but ever since Shi
decided to go to Ning'an Temple

31:28.750 --> 31:29.960
to pray for a month,

31:30.040 --> 31:31.120
my heart

31:31.140 --> 31:32.780
has been pounding.

31:33.600 --> 31:35.590
You just miss Young Master Shi.

31:35.920 --> 31:37.520
Look, you're about to see him now.

31:37.520 --> 31:38.780
Stop worrying so much.

31:38.920 --> 31:39.790
Yes.

31:39.790 --> 31:41.070
Shi has always been

31:41.070 --> 31:42.630
an obedient child.

31:43.680 --> 31:44.880
Perhaps it's just that

31:44.880 --> 31:46.520
my body is failing me.

31:47.170 --> 31:47.690
Come on.

31:49.850 --> 31:50.990
Let's go! Come on!

32:13.940 --> 32:15.210
It's fine. It's not dirty.

32:15.210 --> 32:16.550
Be careful.

32:16.840 --> 32:17.710
These herbs

32:17.740 --> 32:18.850
are very precious.

32:37.280 --> 32:38.610
Young Master Zheng Shi.

32:38.690 --> 32:40.220
Actually, you don't have to

32:41.000 --> 32:42.400
pound the herbs so hard.

32:42.790 --> 32:43.870
At this rate,

32:43.900 --> 32:45.550
the table will collapse

32:45.570 --> 32:47.230
before the medicine is ready.

32:52.240 --> 32:52.920
Fan Yun.

32:54.510 --> 32:55.290
How much of this

32:55.290 --> 32:56.420
should I put in?

32:57.720 --> 32:58.650
About that much.

32:59.550 --> 33:00.150
This much?

33:00.240 --> 33:01.100
That's enough.

33:02.880 --> 33:03.920
I didn't expect

33:04.440 --> 33:06.100
the Second Young Master Zheng

33:06.240 --> 33:08.040
to come help out in the pharmacy.

33:28.690 --> 33:29.850
Support from all cities

33:29.850 --> 33:30.930
has arrived.

33:31.890 --> 33:33.050
We have also told

33:33.070 --> 33:35.440
the people how to make the medicine.

33:36.000 --> 33:36.790
I think

33:37.000 --> 33:37.860
it won't be long

33:38.270 --> 33:40.270
before the plague is under control.

33:40.310 --> 33:41.240
Then,

33:42.070 --> 33:43.480
we can return to Ling'an.

33:45.620 --> 33:46.450
No,

33:47.270 --> 33:49.270
I mean I can

33:49.440 --> 33:51.300
return to Ling'an to report back.

33:53.360 --> 33:54.890
Aren't we in this together?

34:02.160 --> 34:03.160
You must be tired.

34:03.670 --> 34:06.120
I happen to have brought
some specialty tea from Jing City.

34:06.120 --> 34:07.290
Would you like to try it?

34:07.290 --> 34:07.990
Sure.

34:08.880 --> 34:11.340
They say Jing City's tea
is world-renowned.

34:11.400 --> 34:13.230
The tea in your hands must be

34:13.510 --> 34:15.070
the best of the best.

34:38.429 --> 34:40.030
Did you spill it on the herbs?

34:41.460 --> 34:43.260
Do you only care about the herbs?

34:44.040 --> 34:45.290
I burned my hand.

34:50.940 --> 34:53.370
I'm just worried about
these medicinal herbs.

34:53.370 --> 34:54.670
They're already scarce.

34:54.670 --> 34:55.870
If we lose more,

34:55.960 --> 34:57.590
how can we treat the people?

35:00.120 --> 35:01.120
Fan Yun, don't go.

35:06.240 --> 35:08.170
Sit here. I'll make the tea for you.

35:11.670 --> 35:12.370
Alright.

35:12.570 --> 35:13.820
Thank you then.

35:31.890 --> 35:33.290
There are usually people

35:33.480 --> 35:35.340
who do these things for me at home.

35:35.510 --> 35:37.370
I'm... not very familiar with it.

35:39.290 --> 35:40.730
I can tell.

35:55.340 --> 35:56.810
Alright, Young Master Zheng Shi.

35:56.810 --> 35:57.830
Why don't you

35:58.060 --> 35:59.420
just leave it to me?

36:13.390 --> 36:16.120
What are they whispering about
alone in the room?

36:21.100 --> 36:21.820
I can't hear anythi...

36:21.820 --> 36:23.510
What's Your Excellency listening to?

36:23.510 --> 36:24.470
You scared me!

36:25.930 --> 36:27.930
You nearly committed the crime
of murdering the governor.

36:27.930 --> 36:29.590
Forgive me, Your Excellency!

36:33.350 --> 36:34.010
Never mind.

36:34.400 --> 36:35.730
What are you doing here?

36:35.920 --> 36:38.110
I came to ask Lady Fan Yun for some herbs.

36:38.110 --> 36:39.590
Why's Your Excellency lingering here

36:39.590 --> 36:40.720
instead of going in?

36:42.710 --> 36:43.760
I'm...

36:43.760 --> 36:44.590
taking a walk.

36:45.670 --> 36:46.530
Go do your work.

36:47.070 --> 36:47.710
OK.

36:53.910 --> 36:54.460
Suyin.

36:54.890 --> 36:55.850
Do me a favor.

36:57.130 --> 36:58.600
Take this bowl of hot congee

36:58.600 --> 37:00.000
to Fan Yun,

37:00.280 --> 37:01.430
and tell her that

37:01.450 --> 37:02.500
tonight, I'll be

37:02.750 --> 37:04.480
waiting for her at the city gate

37:04.530 --> 37:05.510
until she comes.

37:05.940 --> 37:06.870
Got it?

37:09.230 --> 37:09.880
Go.

37:10.340 --> 37:13.270
Why doesn't Your Excellency
deliver it personally?

37:15.670 --> 37:17.000
Young Master Zheng Shi,

37:17.190 --> 37:18.350
so you've really

37:18.590 --> 37:20.450
never done a single chore before.

37:20.920 --> 37:22.580
I've been treasuring this tea

37:23.360 --> 37:25.160
and never shared it with anyone.

37:26.320 --> 37:27.380
It's sweet dew tea.

37:29.760 --> 37:30.240
Go now.

37:30.270 --> 37:31.070
Don't forget!

37:33.960 --> 37:34.810
Suyin?

37:37.790 --> 37:38.830
Why are you here?

37:39.250 --> 37:39.680
I...

37:40.440 --> 37:42.700
I came to ask for some herbs,
Lady Fan Yun.

37:42.880 --> 37:44.420
But His Ex...

37:46.990 --> 37:47.720
Suyin.

37:47.750 --> 37:49.410
You can't even pass a message.

37:50.100 --> 37:51.060
This is crazy.

37:51.770 --> 37:52.730
What's wrong?

37:53.880 --> 37:54.800
His...

37:55.140 --> 37:56.490
-His...
-His?

37:56.510 --> 37:57.510
His...

37:58.200 --> 37:59.150
His...

38:01.590 --> 38:02.750
-Tian Xing!
-Your Excellency?

38:02.750 --> 38:03.710
You must be hungry.

38:03.710 --> 38:05.020
-I'll bring you food!
-Qi Zheng!

38:05.020 --> 38:06.150
Where are you going?

38:10.030 --> 38:11.290
What's wrong with him?

38:12.100 --> 38:12.980
I don't know.

38:15.920 --> 38:17.560
He was acting so weird.
